description: Feature Description : Verifying Login functionality for ITOpsAdmin

steps.name: User with ITOps role renders the URL
user enters Username as "Itops_admin", Password as "qa123" and clicks on Login button

description: Feature Description: ITOpsAdmin verifies Alert Correlation Policy operations
name: Verify Alert Correlation Policy

elements.name: ITOps Admin creates Alert Correlation policy

steps.name: "Admin" enters project name as "Automation_IB_24" in the search field
Admin selects "policy" attribute as "Business Time Alert"
Admin clicks on Save and Add Rule button

elements.name: ITOps Admin adds Alert Correlation rule

steps.name: Admin selects "rule" attribute as "Business Time Alert"
Admin clicks on Activate Policy toggle button
Admin clicks on Yes button in confirmation popup
verify column values in Policy listing page

elements.name: ITOps Admin edits existing Alert Correlation policy from viewMode

steps.name: Admin clicks on edit policy button
Admin enters "Alert Correlation" Policy Name as "Automation IB"
Admin clicks on Yes button in confirmation popup
verify "success" toaster "The alert correlation policy change will not have any effect on any existing alert clusters"
Admin enters "Alert Correlation" rule name as "CorrelationRuleUpdated"
Admin clicks on Yes button in confirmation popup
verify "success" toaster "The alert correlation policy change will not have any effect on any existing alert clusters"

elements.name: ITOps Admin edits existing Alert Correlation Policy from Listing page

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on edit icon in listing page "Automation IB"
Admin enters "Alert Correlation" Policy Name as "Automation IB"
Admin selects "policy" attribute as "Business Time Alert"
Admin clicks on Yes button in confirmation popup
verify "success" toaster "on any existing alert clusters"
Admin enters "Alert Correlation" rule name as "CorrelationRuleUpdated1"
Admin selects "rule" attribute as "Business Time Alert"
Admin clicks on Yes button in confirmation popup
verify "success" toaster "on any existing alert clusters"

elements.name: Admin deletes the existing Alert Correlation Policy

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on delete icon in listing page "Automation IB"
Admin clicks on Yes button in confirmation popup
"Admin" verifies if "Policy deleted successfully" message is displayed
